General Note Regarding Groups

It is unheard of for members of the Illuminati to betray the Illuminati.

For the Nobody it is a much different story. As they progress they discover
that they are unable to trust anybody. Even amongst the groups that he is
shares an affinity with there are Illuminati agents that have infiltrated
(undetectably) them.

All adversaries and allies come in a unpredicatable and all encompassing
array of genders, races, religions, jobs, appearances, sexual orientations,
etc. 
